      "span_text": "ADAMTS-1 is the first member of the disintegrin-like and metalloproteinase with thrombospondin type I motifs (ADAMTS) family, and is characterized by having an ADAM metalloproteinase domain and thrombospondin type I motifs [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ."
